title: Party Organizations
new-page: true
is-card: true
tags: party_affairs
view-if: party_organizations_timer <= 0
on-arrival: month_actions += 1; party_organizations_timer = 6;
card-image: img/organization.png
max-visits: 6

= Party Organizations

In addition to being a political party, the <span style="color: #990000;">**PNI**</span> is a social world onto itself, with a vast array of associated organizations which serve the social needs of their members from cradle to grave.

- @newspaper: Launch our own newspaper, run by the party.
- @newspapers: Fund our newspapers and journalists.
- @welfare: Finance more mutual aid and welfare programs.
- @schools: Support the *Taman Siswa* schools.
- @youth: Allocate funds to our youth organizations.
- @nothing: Do not increase funding for any program.
- @easy_discard

@newspaper
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -2 resources. All major parties have their own affiliated newspaper except for us.
on-arrival: resources -= 2; newspaper = 1;

{!<div style="display: flex;justify-content: left;">
<img src="img/suluh.jpeg" style="width: 100px;border: 5px solid var(--card-border-color);margin: 10px"> 
<div style="width: 300px;">We have launched our own weekly newspaper veritably named "<span class="tooltip-text" title="Torch of Indonesia">*Suluh Indonesia*</span>". We can utilize this as one of our campaign media, effectively garnering support, especially among the middle class.</div>
</div>!}

@newspapers
view-if: newspaper = 1
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources
on-arrival: resources -= 1; media_timer = 0;
go-to: media

@welfare
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources
on-arrival: resources -= 1; workers_aid += 1; workers_pni += 4*(1 - dissent); unemployed_pni += 5*(1 - dissent);

We have increased funding to Workers' Welfare. [? if black_thursday_seen > 0 : In an age of economic crisis, this will be helpful for improving our standing among the unemployed. ?]

@schools
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources. We shall support the education of the future generation of patriots.
face-image: img/taman_siswa.jpg
on-arrival: resources -= 1; taman_siswa += 1; left_dissent -= 6; center_dissent -= 6; labor_dissent -= 6; reformist_dissent -= 6; 

*Taman Siswa* was founded by Ki Hadjar Dewantara as form of struggle against the colonizers, not through physical struggle nor politics, rather through education and culture. By supporting these schools we can usher in a new generation of bright-minded patriots.

#to do: boost overall national education

@youth
choose-if: resources > 0
unavailable-subtitle: Not enough resources.
subtitle: -1 resources. We have the reputation of being a party of veterans. We can change that.
on-arrival: resources -= 1; young_marhaenists += 1; partindo_strength += 5; wilopo_strength += 5; radicalization += 1;

We have funded our youth organizations: the <span style="color: #990000;">Indonesian Democratic Youth</span> and the <span style="color: #990000;">Marhaenist Youth Movement</span>. Their membership count has increased so as the <span style="color: #990000;">**PNI**</span>'s. Our new young members flock to the <span style="color: #7c0000;">Radicalist</span> wing of the party, though some of the more educated youth have joined the <span style="color: #ff6d50;">Moderates</span>. 

@nothing

We do not fund any party organizations.

- @return: Continue...
